data.description: This centrally located single-family pool home offers 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, a convenient laundry room, and a brand new AC. It also features a screened-in pool & patio, a shed with electricity, fenced in yard, and a one car garage. Don't miss out on this opportunity to have your own private pool while living minutes from the beaches, shopping, and the highway. It is the perfect blend of convenience and coastal living!
